icod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`  \n  - Verify: Enum with +kubebuilder:validation:Enum marker\n\n- [ ] **T7** Define `ContainerTemplateSpec` supporting type  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n  - Fields: Image, Command, Args, Env, Resources, RuntimeClassName  \n  - Verify: Required Image field with proper markers\n\n- [ ] **T8** Add CodeInterpreter types to register.go  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`  \n  - Add `&CodeInterpreter{}` and `&CodeInterpreterList{}` to AddKnownTypes  \n  - Verify: Both types registered in scheme\n\n- [ ] **T9** Generate DeepCopy methods  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`  \n  - Use: `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/...`  \n  - Verify: DeepCopyInto and DeepCopy methods generated for all types\n\n- [ ] **T10** Write unit tests for CodeInterpreter types  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`  \n  - Coverage: Type instantiation, DeepCopy, defaults validation  \n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` passes\n\n- [ ] **T11** Verify types compile correctly  \n  - Command: `go build ./pkg/apis/...`  \n  - Verify: No compilation errors\n\n- [ ] **T12** Run linter on API types  \n  - Command: `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/...` or `go vet ./pkg/apis/...`  \n  - Verify: No linting errors\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n```\nT1 → T2 → T3 → T4 → T5 → T6 → T7 → T8 → T9 → T10 → T11 → T12\n```\n\n**Parallel:** T6, T7 can be done in parallel with T4, T5\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter CRD type defined in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter includes spec: authMode, maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, ports, template, warmPoolSize\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter includes status: conditions, observedGeneration, ready\n- [ ] All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n- [ ] DeepCopy methods generated and compile correctly\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n- [ ] `go vet ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n- [ ] Unit tests pass\n\n---\n\n# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] **T1** 定义 `TargetPort` 共享结构体（端口配置）\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 字段: Port, Protocol, Name, PathPrefix\n  - 验证: 类型定义正确，JSON tag 完整\n\n- [ ] **T2** 定义 `PodTemplateSpec` 共享结构体（Pod 模板）\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 验证: 嵌入 metav1.ObjectMeta，可选 Spec 引用 PodSpec\n\n- [ ] **T3** 定义 `PodSpec` 共享结构体（Pod 规范子集）\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 字段: Containers, Volumes, RestartPolicy, ServiceAccountName, NodeSelector, Affinity, Tolerations 等\n  - 验证: 所有字段正确从 corev1.PodSpec 引用\n\n- [ ] **T4** 定义 `ContainerSpec` 共享结构体（容器规范子集）\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 字段: Name, Image, Command, Args, Env, Resources, Ports 等\n  - 验证: 包含容器核心字段\n\n- [ ] **T5** 定义 `AuthMode` 类型及常量\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 常量: `AuthModePicod = \"picod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`\n  - 验证: 类型定义和常量值正确\n\n- [ ] **T6** 为 TargetPort 添加 kubebuilder 验证标记\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 验证: Port 范围 1-65535, Protocol 枚举 HTTP/HTTPS\n\n- [ ] **T7** 为 PodSpec 字段添加可选标记\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 验证: 所有字段标记 +optional\n\n- [ ] **T8** 为 ContainerSpec 字段添加验证标记\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n  - 验证: Name 和 Image 标记为 required\n\n- [ ] **T9** 运行 deep copy 生成\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n  - 命令: `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/...`\n  - 验证: 所有共享类型的 DeepCopy 方法已生成\n\n- [ ] **T10** 验证共享类型编译正确\n  - 命令: `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n  - 验证: 无编译错误\n\n- [ ] **T11** 运行 linter 检查\n  - 命令: `go vet ./pkg/apis/...`\n  - 验证: 无 lint 错误\n\n- [ ] **T12** 编写共享类型单元测试\n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n  - 验证: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` 通过\n\n---\n\n## 依赖关系\n\n```\nT1 ─┬─> T6 ─> T9 ─> T10 ─> T11 ─> T12\nT2 ─┤\nT3 ─┤\nT4 ─┤\nT5 ─┘\nT7 ─> T9\nT8 ─> 